{
  "sourceLanguage": "zh-Hans",
  "strings": {
    "Niche %@": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Niche %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Niche %@ 已可安装（一键自动安装）。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Niche %@ is ready to install (one-click automatic install)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Niche 会在访达中选中此文件夹。在访达里右键选择「自定义文件夹」,即可设置符号、emoji 或颜色。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Niche will select this folder in Finder. Right-click it there and choose “Customize Folder” to set a symbol, emoji, or color."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」不存在或已被移动": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" doesn't exist or has been moved"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」已存在": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" Already Exists"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「显示简介」需要让 Niche 控制「访达」。请在「系统设置 › 隐私与安全性 › 自动化」中允许 Niche 控制访达,然后重试。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“Get Info” requires Niche to control Finder. Please allow Niche to control Finder in System Settings › Privacy & Security › Automation, then try again."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "不再提示": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Don’t Ask Again"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "两者都保留": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Keep Both"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "临时:%@": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Temporary: %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "从刘海滑出后,每个绑定文件夹是一个 tab。拖动可调整顺序。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Once it slides out from the notch, each bound folder becomes a tab. Drag to reorder."
          }
        }
      }
    },
